== Amzruy ==
Teṭṭaf tutlayt tamaziɣt tamzwarut kra n tɣawsiwin ur illin ɣ [[tutlayin tifrusyawiyin]] yaḍnin, macc [[tutlayin timaziɣin]] n ɣil-ad mmrwasnt bahra ɣ ingratsn. Tbayn-d tutlayt tamaziɣt tamzwarut ɣar 3000 isggʷasn aya mqqar tbḍa f [[Tutlayin tifrusyawiyin]]t gr 9000 d 10,000 n isggʷasn aya. Iɣ d-nucka ad nẓṛ mad tettini tussna n usmzazal n tutlayin d [[Amzruy|umzruy]]<ref>-{Militarev, A. (1984), "Sovremennoe sravnitel'no-istoricheskoe afrazijskoe jazykoznanie: chto ono mozhet dat' istoricheskoj nauke?", ''Lingvisticheskaja rekonstrukcija i drevnejshaja istorija Vostoka'', Moscow, pp. 3–26, 44–5}-</ref>, rad naf is nnan imassann mas tzri tutlayt ad f sin tikliwin n tmhazt ad tn igan<ref>-{Louali & Philippson 2003, "''Les Protoméditerranéens Capsiens sont-ils des protoberbères ? Interrogations de linguiste.''", GALF (Groupement des Anthropologues de Langue Française), Mrrakc، 22-25 Cutanbir 2003.}-

↑</ref>:

* Tamaziɣt tamzwarut '''1''' ('''-{PB1}-''') nna yumann kra n 7000 n isggʷasn aya.
* Tamaziɣt tamzwarut '''2''' ('''-{PB2}-''') tad tga illis n ('''PB1'''), d nttat a ɣ d uckant akkʷ tutlayin timaziɣin lli sul illan ɣil-ad.

Ɣ tasut tis-30 dat n tlalit n Ɛisa, bḍan middn lli sawalnin s tmaziɣt tamzwarut ɣ tfriqt n ugafa gr [[Lmɣrib]] d [[Miṣra]]. Ɣ tasut tis-10 qbl ad iggz ɛisa, ijṛa yan ttawassuɛ yaḍn nttan ad aɣ iskrn ma mi nttini ɣil-a igdudn [[imaziɣn]] lli-nn iqyydn ɣ dar irumiyn. Ijra ttawassuɛ iggʷran ɣ ifḍ d kra bɛd ɛisa, lliɣ nnucgn imuhaɣ nɣ itwargiyn lli yumẓn ɣil-a tanzruft imqqurn n tfriqt lli mu nttini Ṣṣaḥra.<ref>-{Heine 2000, p. 292.}-</ref>

